{"tid":1587714,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方正驅散旺角警署一帶示威者","createTime":"2019-09-22T13:51:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T13:58:06.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"04a25abdacce99f2379205bdffa439d074d7ebce","tid":1587714,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:51:30.000Z","msg":"電台及電視台當值宣布員注意：<br />\n <br />\n請盡快播出下列消息，並在適當時間重播：<br />\n <br />\n  激進示威者今日（九月二十二日）集結在旺角警署附近一帶的馬路，並向警署投擲磚頭及以鐳射光線照射在場警務人員。<br />\n   <br />\n  警方正使用相應武力驅散，警告示威者立即停止違法行為及離去。<br />\n   <br />\n  警方提醒附近一帶市民留意最新情況，如有需要，盡量留在室內安全地方，並關好窗戶。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年9月22日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間21時43分"},{"pid":"477b89a6a63be81dfbcc3bf94b21073bdb30ac1c","tid":1587714,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:51:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201909/22/P2019092200883.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201909%2F22%2FP2019092200883.htm&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBje9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=8707db6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201909/22/P2019092200883.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8c2ac682701f51754905e448e43d49f9a2f85526","tid":1587714,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:51:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7fc6807994d434e66f045dd8a7d7d97b8597cf33","tid":1587714,"uid":253345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:58:06.000Z","msg":"一定要平安走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}